  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Change in quality of life as measured by SQOLS</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline to 4 weeks, baseline to 8 weeks post ostomy belt use</time_frame>
    <description>Quality of life will be assessed using the Stoma Quality of Life Scale questionnaire (SQOLS) with a range in score from 0 to 100 in overall satisfaction in life with a higher score indicating higher satisfaction.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
