      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Current patients at University of Miami Hospital with stoma willing to trial an ostomy&#xD;
             belt&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  18 - 70 years old&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Willing and able to sign informed consent&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Patients without stoma or unwilling to wear ostomy belt.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Have any condition that, in the opinion of the investigator, would compromise the&#xD;
             well-being of the patient or the study or prevent the patient from meeting or&#xD;
             performing study requirements.&#xD;
      </textblock>
